# Architecture

**Organization**: flat


## Module Boundaries

Key modules:

- `docs` — Documentation
- `src` — Source code
- `src/product_builders/models` — Data models / entities
- `tests` — Test files


## Source Layout

- `src/`

> Place new code in the appropriate directory following the existing structure.

## Rules

1. Follow the existing module organization — do not restructure without explicit approval
2. Keep dependencies flowing in one direction (see module boundaries above)
3. New modules should follow the same patterns as existing ones
4. Shared utilities go in the designated utilities/helpers directory
